- app dir contains the app image code
- app sends back headers in response
- k8s dir contains pod & service def for app as well as nginx
- nginx conf if monted as a volume so that conf can be changed locally 
- url is http://<host-ip>:30001/fdapp
- request with json payload curl --request POST --data '{"testkey":"testvalue"}' -H "Content-Type: application/json" http://<IP>
- request with header curl --request POST --data '{"testkey":"testvalue"}' -H "Content-Type: application/json" http://<IP>
